lead_paragraph: This festival featured a resurgence of analog methods after an era of all-too-neat digital sounds.

headline.print_headline: A Show of What Man and Machine Can Accomplish
headline.main: At Moogfest, a Demonstration of What Human and Machine Can Accomplish

snippet: This festival featured a resurgence of analog methods after an era of all-too-neat digital sounds.
abstract: Jon Pareles Critic's Notebook remarks on lineup and performances at Moogfest 2016, four-day music and tech festival organized by synthesizer firm Moog Music in Durham, NC.
